#: apps/remix/app/routes/_unauthenticated+/articles.signature-disclosure.tsx
msgid ""
"By using the electronic signature feature, you are consenting to conduct "
"transactions and receive disclosures electronically. You acknowledge that "
"your electronic signature on documents is binding and that you accept the "
"terms outlined in the documents you are signing."
msgstr ""
"Используя функцию электронной подписи, вы соглашаетесь проводить транзакции "
